t;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Foto karakter Ibu di kasur yang disebarkan Joko Anwar di akun Twitter dan Instagramnya untuk dijadikan meme (sumber: Twitter) \" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Foto karakter Ibu di kasur yang disebarkan Joko Anwar di akun Twitter dan Instagramnya untuk dijadikan meme (sumber: Twitter) &lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mem7-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mem7.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46060\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mem7.jpg\" alt=\"Foto karakter Ibu di kasur yang disebarkan Joko Anwar di akun Twitter dan Instagramnya untuk dijadikan meme (sumber: Twitter) \" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mem7.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mem7-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46060\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Foto karakter Ibu di kasur yang disebarkan Joko Anwar di akun Twitter dan Instagramnya untuk dijadikan meme (sumber: Twitter)</p></div></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46058\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46058\" data-attachment-id=\"46058\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/kesan-awal-tv-anime-terbaru-lupin-third-part-5/attachment/mem4/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mem4.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Salah satu meme parodi Pengabdi Setan. (Sumber: Twitter)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Salah satu meme parodi Pengabdi Setan. (Sumber: Twitter)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mem4-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mem4.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46058\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mem4.jpg\" alt=\"Salah satu meme parodi Pengabdi Setan. (Sumber: Twitter)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mem4.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mem4-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46058\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Salah satu meme parodi Pengabdi Setan. (Sumber: Twitter)</p></div></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46056\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46056\" data-attachment-id=\"46056\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/kesan-awal-tv-anime-terbaru-lupin-third-part-5/attachment/mem2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mem2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Salah satu meme parodi Pengabdi Setan dari gambar yang dikirimkan Joko Anwar di akunnya, (sumber: Brilio) \" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mem2-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mem2.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46056\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mem2.jpg\" alt=\"Salah satu meme parodi Pengabdi Setan dari gambar yang dikirimkan Joko Anwar di akunnya, (sumber: Brilio) \" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mem2.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mem2-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46056\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Salah satu meme parodi Pengabdi Setan dari gambar yang dikirimkan Joko Anwar di akunnya, (sumber: Brilio)</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>***</em></p>\n<p>Setelah Joko Anwar, rumah produksi Starvision dan Visinema Pictures ikut menyeriusi meme, di mana mereka melakukan kontes meme untuk film mereka masing-masing, yaitu Susah Sinyal dan <em>Love For Sale</em>.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46063\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46063\" data-attachment-id=\"46063\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/kesan-awal-tv-anime-terbaru-lupin-third-part-5/attachment/mrm6/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mrm6.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"sumber: Instagram\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;sumber: Instagram&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mrm6-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mrm6.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46063\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mrm6.jpg\" alt=\"sumber: Instagram\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mrm6.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mrm6-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46063\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">sumber: Instagram</p></div></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46057\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46057\" data-attachment-id=\"46057\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/kesan-awal-tv-anime-terbaru-lupin-third-part-5/attachment/mem3/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mem3.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"sumber: Instagram\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;sumber: Instagram&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mem3-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mem3.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46057\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mem3.jpg\" alt=\"sumber: Instagram\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mem3.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/mem3-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46057\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">sumber: Instagram</p></div></p>\n<p>Namun sayang, langkah Starvision dan Visinema Pictures menyeriusi meme ini mungkin kurang berhasil. Karena meme film Susah Sinyal dan Love For Sale pada akhirnya tidak berujung viral seperti meme-meme film Pengabdi Setan. Jumlah penonton Lover For Sale pun tidak begitu memuaskan karena ‘hanya’ mencapai kurang dari 200.000 (berbeda dengan Susah Sinyal yang masih beruntung mendapatkan dua juta lebih penonton karena tayang akhir tahun).</p>\n<p>Mungkin sebagai evaluasi, ke depannya para sutradara dan produser perlu dengan cerdik mengambil sisi <em>memeable </em>dari film mereka, atau bahkan membuat dengan sengaja adegan yang <em>memeable </em>itu sendiri.</p>\n<p>Karena meme bukan sekedar meme, atau jika kita kembali ke istilah aslinya&#8211;meme adalah sebuah tren, sebuah viral. Bagaimana menurut kalian?</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"915d957c-39a9-515d-8df6-4616fcf8f437"}}}